{
  "video_id": "yNhu0MG_2MA",
  "title": "The new age of corporate monopolies | Margrethe Vestager",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 17000.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s go back to 1957."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18680.0,
      "end_time": 22695.0,
      "text": "Representatives from six European countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22720.0,
      "end_time": 24456.0,
      "text": "had come to Rome"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 27760.0,
      "text": "to sign the treaty that was to create the European Union."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29840.0,
      "end_time": 31280.0,
      "text": "Europe was destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32560.000000000004,
      "end_time": 36800.0,
      "text": "A world war had emerged from Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37280.0,
      "end_time": 39936.0,
      "text": "The human suffering was unbelievable"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39960.0,
      "end_time": 41680.0,
      "text": "and unprecedented."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43720.0,
      "end_time": 45696.0,
      "text": "Those men"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45720.0,
      "end_time": 49856.0,
      "text": "wanted to create a peaceful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49880.0,
      "end_time": 52960.0,
      "text": "democratic Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52120.0,
      "end_time": 54280.0,
      "text": "a Europe that works for its people."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55760.0,
      "end_time": 58576.0,
      "text": "And one of the many building blocks"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58600.0,
      "end_time": 60856.0,
      "text": "in that peace project"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60880.0,
      "end_time": 62920.0,
      "text": "was a common European market."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65800.0,
      "end_time": 67216.0,
      "text": "Already back then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67240.0,
      "end_time": 69560.0,
      "text": "they saw how markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69800.0,
      "end_time": 71416.0,
      "text": "when left to themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71440.0,
      "end_time": 76495.0,
      "text": "can sort of slip into being just the private property"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76519.0,
      "end_time": 79240.0,
      "text": "of big businesses and cartels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80360.0,
      "end_time": 82560.0,
      "text": "meeting the needs of some businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83520.0,
      "end_time": 86280.0,
      "text": "and not the needs of customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 87840.0,
      "end_time": 89760.0,
      "text": "So from our very first day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90680.0,
      "end_time": 92320.0,
      "text": "in 1957,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93360.0,
      "end_time": 96216.0,
      "text": "the European Union had rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96240.0,
      "end_time": 98559.0,
      "text": "to defend fair competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99680.0,
      "end_time": 102976.0,
      "text": "And that means competition on the merits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 106216.0,
      "text": "that you compete on the quality of your products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106240.0,
      "end_time": 108175.0,
      "text": "the prices you can offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108200.0,
      "end_time": 111360.0,
      "text": "the services, the innovation that you produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112400.0,
      "end_time": 115216.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s competition on the merits."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115240.0,
      "end_time": 118520.0,
      "text": "You have a fair chance of making it on such a market."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119320.0,
      "end_time": 121336.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s my job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121360.0,
      "end_time": 124136.0,
      "text": "as Commissioner for Competition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124160.0,
      "end_time": 127856.0,
      "text": "to make sure that companies who do business in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127880.0,
      "end_time": 129919.0,
      "text": "live by those rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132360.0,
      "end_time": 134360.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s take a step back."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136320.0,
      "end_time": 139959.0,
      "text": "Why do we need rules on competition at all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140880.0,
      "end_time": 143680.0,
      "text": "Why not just let businesses compete?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144600.0,
      "end_time": 147296.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t that also the best for us"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147320.0,
      "end_time": 149616.0,
      "text": "if they compete freely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 149640.0,
      "end_time": 151896.0,
      "text": "since more competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 151920.0,
      "end_time": 154950.0,
      "text": "drives more quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154120.0,
      "end_time": 156640.0,
      "text": "lower prices, more innovation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159800.0,
      "end_time": 161280.0,
      "text": "Well, mostly it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163520.0,
      "end_time": 168296.0,
      "text": "But the problem is that sometimes, for businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168320.0,
      "end_time": 172239.0,
      "text": "competition can be inconvenient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175120.0,
      "end_time": 178800.0,
      "text": "because competition means that the race is never over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179760.0,
      "end_time": 181280.0,
      "text": "the game is never won."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 182400.0,
      "end_time": 185560.0,
      "text": "No matter how well you were doing in the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 185800.0,
      "end_time": 186896.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s always someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 186920.0,
      "end_time": 190200.0,
      "text": "who are out there wanting to take your place."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 192360.0,
      "end_time": 195536.0,
      "text": "So the temptation to avoid competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195560.0,
      "end_time": 196760.0,
      "text": "is powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 198320.0,
      "end_time": 202560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s rooted in motives as old as Adam and Eve:"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 203800.0,
      "end_time": 206560.0,
      "text": "in greed for yet more money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 211950.0,
      "text": "in fear of losing your position in the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 213760.0,
      "text": "and all the benefits it brings."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 215960.0,
      "end_time": 218896.0,
      "text": "And when greed and fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 218920.0,
      "end_time": 220775.0,
      "text": "are linked to power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 220800.0,
      "end_time": 222360.0,
      "text": "you have a dangerous mix."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 224280.0,
      "end_time": 226800.0,
      "text": "We see that in political life."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227360.0,
      "end_time": 229216.0,
      "text": "In part of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 229240.0,
      "end_time": 231616.0,
      "text": "the mix of greed and fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 231640.0,
      "end_time": 234256.0,
      "text": "means that those who get power"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 234280.0,
      "end_time": 238720.0,
      "text": "become reluctant to give it back."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 240920.0,
      "end_time": 242456.0,
      "text": "One of the many things"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 242480.0,
      "end_time": 247215.0,
      "text": "I like and admire in our democracies"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 247240.0,
      "end_time": 249560.0,
      "text": "are the norms"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 249800.0,
      "end_time": 252256.0,
      "text": "that make our leaders hand over power"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 252280.0,
      "end_time": 253880.0,
      "text": "when voters tell them to."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 256720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259840.00000000003,
      "text": "And competition rules can do a similar thing in the market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 260920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265760.0,
      "text": "making sure that greed and fear doesn&#39;t overcome fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 267600.0,
      "end_time": 269136.0,
      "text": "Because those rules mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 274000.0,
      "text": "that companies cannot misuse their power to undermine competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 276400.0,
      "end_time": 278640.0,
      "text": "Think for a moment about your car."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 280720.0,
      "end_time": 284256.0,
      "text": "It has thousands of parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284280.0,
      "end_time": 287655.0,
      "text": "from the foam that makes the seats"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 287680.0,
      "end_time": 290800.0,
      "text": "to the electrical wiring to the light bulbs."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 291680.0,
      "end_time": 293976.0,
      "text": "And for many of those parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294000.0,
      "end_time": 295576.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s carmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 295600.0,
      "end_time": 298640.0,
      "text": "they are dependent on only a few suppliers."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 301120.0,
      "end_time": 303656.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s hardly surprising"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 303680.0,
      "end_time": 307736.0,
      "text": "that it is kind of tempting for those suppliers"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 307760.0,
      "end_time": 310200.0,
      "text": "to come together and fix prices."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 311920.0,
      "end_time": 313816.0,
      "text": "But just imagine what that could do"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 313840.0,
      "end_time": 318760.0,
      "text": "to the final price of your new car in the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 320520.0,
      "end_time": 322960.0,
      "text": "Except, it&#39;s not imaginary."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 324400.0,
      "end_time": 326575.0,
      "text": "The European Commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 326600.0,
      "end_time": 332456.0,
      "text": "has dealt with already seven different car parts cartels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 332480.0,
      "end_time": 334560.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re still investigating some."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 336320.0,
      "end_time": 339496.0,
      "text": "Here, the Department of Justice"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 339520.0,
      "end_time": 342159.0,
      "text": "are also looking into the market for car parts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 342920.0,
      "end_time": 346456.0,
      "text": "and it has called it the biggest criminal investigation"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 346480.0,
      "end_time": 348200.0,
      "text": "it has ever pursued."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 349320.0,
      "end_time": 351736.0,
      "text": "But without competition rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 351760.0,
      "end_time": 354216.0,
      "text": "there would be no investigation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 354240.0,
      "end_time": 358136.0,
      "text": "and there would be nothing to stop this collusion from happening"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 358160.0,
      "end_time": 360800.0,
      "text": "and the prices of your car to go up."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 363600.0,
      "end_time": 365936.0,
      "text": "Yet it&#39;s not only companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 365960.0,
      "end_time": 367760.0,
      "text": "who can undermine fair competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 368960.0,
      "end_time": 370479.0,
      "text": "Governments can do it, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 371720.0,
      "end_time": 375896.0,
      "text": "And governments do that when they hand out subsidies"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 375920.0,
      "end_time": 379480.0,
      "text": "to just the favorite few, the selected."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 381240.0,
      "end_time": 384296.0,
      "text": "They may do that when they hand out subsidies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 384320.0,
      "end_time": 387560.0,
      "text": "and, of course, all financed by taxpayers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 388680.0,
      "end_time": 389880.0,
      "text": "to companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390760.0,
      "end_time": 395695.0,
      "text": "That may be in the form of special tax treatments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 395720.0,
      "end_time": 397136.0,
      "text": "like the tax benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 397160.0,
      "end_time": 402560.0,
      "text": "that firms like Fiat, Starbucks and Apple got"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 402800.0,
      "end_time": 403919.0,
      "text": "from some governments in Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 406120.0,
      "end_time": 409680.0,
      "text": "Those subsidies stop companies from competing on equal terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 411240.0,
      "end_time": 414816.0,
      "text": "They can mean that the companies that succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 414840.0,
      "end_time": 417440.0,
      "text": "well, they are the companies that got the most subsidy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 418400.0,
      "end_time": 420695.0,
      "text": "the ones that are the best-connected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 420720.0,
      "end_time": 422856.0,
      "text": "and not, as it should be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 422880.0,
      "end_time": 425480.0,
      "text": "the companies that serve consumers the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 427560.0,
      "end_time": 429760.0,
      "text": "So there are times when we need to step in"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 430720.0,
      "end_time": 433920.0,
      "text": "to make sure that competition works the way it should."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 435160.0,
      "end_time": 438360.0,
      "text": "By doing that, we help the market to work fairly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 439720.0,
      "end_time": 444400.0,
      "text": "because competition gives consumers the power to demand a fair deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 445840.0,
      "end_time": 450335.0,
      "text": "It means that companies know that if they cannot offer good prices"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 450360.0,
      "end_time": 452936.0,
      "text": "or the service that&#39;s expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 452960.0,
      "end_time": 456359.0,
      "text": "well, the customers will go somewhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 458680.0,
      "end_time": 461336.0,
      "text": "And that sort of fairness is more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 461360.0,
      "end_time": 463520.0,
      "text": "than we may sometimes realize."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 467560.0,
      "end_time": 470400.0,
      "text": "Very few people think about politics all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 471600.0,
      "end_time": 473760.0,
      "text": "Some even skip it at election time."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 475880.0,
      "end_time": 478376.0,
      "text": "But we are all in the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 478400.0,
      "end_time": 480880.0,
      "text": "Every day, we are in the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 482280.0,
      "end_time": 486520.0,
      "text": "And we don&#39;t want businesses to agree on prices in the back office."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 487520.0,
      "end_time": 490240.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want them to divide the market between them."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 491640.0,
      "end_time": 493536.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t want one big company"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 493560.0,
      "end_time": 496216.0,
      "text": "just to shut out competitors"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 496240.0,
      "end_time": 498400.0,
      "text": "from ever showing us what they can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 500440.0,
      "end_time": 501800.0,
      "text": "If that happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 502760.0,
      "end_time": 506135.0,
      "text": "well, obviously, we feel that someone has cheated us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 506160.0,
      "end_time": 510280.0,
      "text": "that we are being ignored or taken for granted by the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 511680.0,
      "end_time": 515256.0,
      "text": "And that may undermine not only our trust in the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 515280.0,
      "end_time": 517959.0,
      "text": "but also our trust in the society."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 519679.0,
      "end_time": 521616.0,
      "text": "In a recent survey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 521640.0,
      "end_time": 524560.0,
      "text": "more than two-thirds of Europeans"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 524800.0,
      "end_time": 528760.0,
      "text": "said that they had felt the effects of lack of competition:"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 529880.0,
      "end_time": 532240.0,
      "text": "that the price for electricity was too high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 533280.0,
      "end_time": 536480.0,
      "text": "that the price for the medicines they needed was too high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 537560.0,
      "end_time": 539550.0,
      "text": "that they had no real choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 539800.0,
      "end_time": 542416.0,
      "text": "if they wanted to travel by bus or by plane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 542440.0,
      "end_time": 545240.0,
      "text": "or they got poor service from their internet provider."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 546240.0,
      "end_time": 549680.0,
      "text": "In short, they found that the market didn&#39;t treat them fairly."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 551000.0,
      "end_time": 554400.0,
      "text": "And that might seem like very small things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 556000.0,
      "end_time": 558560.0,
      "text": "but they can give you this sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 559720.0,
      "end_time": 561920.0,
      "text": "that the world isn&#39;t really fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 563720.0,
      "end_time": 568576.0,
      "text": "And they see the market, which was supposed to serve everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 568600.0,
      "end_time": 573640.0,
      "text": "become more like the private property of a few powerful companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 575680.0,
      "end_time": 577359.0,
      "text": "The market is not the society."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 578800.0,
      "end_time": 582240.0,
      "text": "Our societies are, of course, much, much more than the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 583720.0,
      "end_time": 586376.0,
      "text": "But lack of trust in the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 586400.0,
      "end_time": 589256.0,
      "text": "can rub off on society"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 589280.0,
      "end_time": 592160.0,
      "text": "so we lose trust in our society as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 595480.0,
      "end_time": 599600.0,
      "text": "And it may be the most important thing we have, trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 601880.0,
      "end_time": 606120.0,
      "text": "We can trust each other if we are treated as equals."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 608800.0,
      "end_time": 612496.0,
      "text": "If we are all to have the same chances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 612520.0,
      "end_time": 616199.0,
      "text": "well, we all have to follow the same fundamental rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 617560.0,
      "end_time": 622239.0,
      "text": "Of course, some people and some businesses are more successful than others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 623360.0,
      "end_time": 625976.0,
      "text": "but we do not trust in a society"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 626000.0,
      "end_time": 628560.0,
      "text": "if the prizes are handed out"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 628800.0,
      "end_time": 630800.0,
      "text": "even before the contest begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 633280.0,
      "end_time": 635680.0,
      "text": "And this is where competition rules come in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 637160.0,
      "end_time": 640656.0,
      "text": "because when we make sure that markets work fairly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 640680.0,
      "end_time": 643896.0,
      "text": "then businesses compete on the merits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 643920.0,
      "end_time": 649175.0,
      "text": "and that helps to build the trust that we need as citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 649200.0,
      "end_time": 652856.0,
      "text": "to feel comfortable and in control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 652880.0,
      "end_time": 656480.0,
      "text": "and the trust that allows our society to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 658000.0,
      "end_time": 661240.0,
      "text": "Because without trust, everything becomes harder."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 662640.0,
      "end_time": 665880.0,
      "text": "Just to live our daily lives, we need to trust in strangers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 667000.0,
      "end_time": 669720.0,
      "text": "to trust the banks who keep our money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 670800.0,
      "end_time": 672520.0,
      "text": "the builders who build our home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 674200.0,
      "end_time": 677256.0,
      "text": "the electrician who comes to fix the wiring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 677280.0,
      "end_time": 679616.0,
      "text": "the doctor who treats us when we&#39;re ill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 679640.0,
      "end_time": 682456.0,
      "text": "not to mention the other drivers on the road,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 682480.0,
      "end_time": 684400.0,
      "text": "and everyone knows that they are crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 686000.0,
      "end_time": 689960.0,
      "text": "And yet, we have to trust them"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 689120.0,
      "end_time": 690480.0,
      "text": "to do the right thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 692120.0,
      "end_time": 695160.0,
      "text": "And the thing is that the more our societies grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 696880.0,
      "end_time": 699896.0,
      "text": "the more important trust becomes"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 699920.0,
      "end_time": 703216.0,
      "text": "and the harder it is to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 703240.0,
      "end_time": 706960.0,
      "text": "And that is a paradox of modern societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 708960.0,
      "end_time": 711296.0,
      "text": "And this is especially true"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 711320.0,
      "end_time": 714120.0,
      "text": "when technology changes the way that we interact."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 715840.0,
      "end_time": 718176.0,
      "text": "Of course, to some degree, technology can help us"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 718200.0,
      "end_time": 722536.0,
      "text": "to build trust in one another with ratings systems and other systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 722560.0,
      "end_time": 724599.0,
      "text": "that enable the sharing economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 726360.0,
      "end_time": 730136.0,
      "text": "But technology also creates completely new challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 730160.0,
      "end_time": 732560.0,
      "text": "when they ask us not to trust in other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 734120.0,
      "end_time": 737840.0,
      "text": "but to trust in algorithms and computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 739920.0,
      "end_time": 743776.0,
      "text": "Of course, we all see and share and appreciate"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 743800.0,
      "end_time": 747776.0,
      "text": "all the good that new technology can do us."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 747800.0,
      "end_time": 749160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a lot of good."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 750240.0,
      "end_time": 755376.0,
      "text": "Autonomous cars can give people with disabilities new independence."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 755400.0,
      "end_time": 756816.0,
      "text": "It can save us all time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 756840.0,
      "end_time": 759520.0,
      "text": "and it can make a much, much better use of resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 761240.0,
      "end_time": 766176.0,
      "text": "Algorithms that rely on crunching enormous amounts of data"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 766200.0,
      "end_time": 770256.0,
      "text": "can enable our doctors to give us a much better treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 770280.0,
      "end_time": 771920.0,
      "text": "and many other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 774440.0,
      "end_time": 778520.0,
      "text": "But no one is going to hand over their medical data"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 779720.0,
      "end_time": 782800.0,
      "text": "or step into a car that&#39;s driven by an algorithm"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 783880.0,
      "end_time": 787439.0,
      "text": "unless they trust the companies that they are dealing with."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 789560.0,
      "end_time": 791920.0,
      "text": "And that trust isn&#39;t always there."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 793240.0,
      "end_time": 797416.0,
      "text": "Today, for example, less than a quarter of Europeans"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 797440.0,
      "end_time": 802800.0,
      "text": "trust online businesses to protect their personal information."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 804720.0,
      "end_time": 806320.0,
      "text": "But what if people knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 807440.0,
      "end_time": 810776.0,
      "text": "that they could rely on technology companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 810800.0,
      "end_time": 812120.0,
      "text": "to treat them fairly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 814280.0,
      "end_time": 816696.0,
      "text": "What if they knew that those companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 816720.0,
      "end_time": 820320.0,
      "text": "respond to competition by trying to do better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 821400.0,
      "end_time": 823680.0,
      "text": "by trying to serve consumers better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 825120.0,
      "end_time": 827456.0,
      "text": "not by using their power"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 827480.0,
      "end_time": 829856.0,
      "text": "to shut out competitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 829880.0,
      "end_time": 832256.0,
      "text": "say, by pushing their services"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 832280.0,
      "end_time": 836160.0,
      "text": "far, far down the list of search results"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 836400.0,
      "end_time": 837800.0,
      "text": "and promoting themselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 839920.0,
      "end_time": 844175.0,
      "text": "What if they knew that compliance with the rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 844200.0,
      "end_time": 847880.0,
      "text": "was built into the algorithms by design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 849800.0,
      "end_time": 851976.0,
      "text": "that the algorithm had to go to competition rules school"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 852000.0,
      "end_time": 853960.0,
      "text": "before they were ever allowed to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 856120.0,
      "end_time": 858856.0,
      "text": "that those algorithms were designed"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 858880.0,
      "end_time": 862496.0,
      "text": "in a way that meant that they couldn&#39;t collude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 862520.0,
      "end_time": 865536.0,
      "text": "that they couldn&#39;t form their own little cartel"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 865560.0,
      "end_time": 867439.0,
      "text": "in the black box they&#39;re working in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 869480.0,
      "end_time": 871280.0,
      "text": "Together with regulation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 872280.0,
      "end_time": 874240.0,
      "text": "competition rules can do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 875240.0,
      "end_time": 877160.0,
      "text": "They can help us to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 877400.0,
      "end_time": 880520.0,
      "text": "that new technology treats people fairly"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 881680.0,
      "end_time": 885160.0,
      "text": "and that everyone can compete on a level playing field."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 886800.0,
      "end_time": 890550.0,
      "text": "And that can help us build the trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 890800.0,
      "end_time": 892496.0,
      "text": "that we need for real innovation"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 892520.0,
      "end_time": 893816.0,
      "text": "to flourish"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 893840.0,
      "end_time": 897440.0,
      "text": "and for societies to develop for citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 899920.0,
      "end_time": 902160.0,
      "text": "Because trust cannot be imposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 903000.0,
      "end_time": 904480.0,
      "text": "It has to be earned."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 906280.0,
      "end_time": 910256.0,
      "text": "Since the very first days of the European Union,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 910280.0,
      "end_time": 911600.0,
      "text": "60 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 912800.0,
      "end_time": 915736.0,
      "text": "our competition rules have helped"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 915760.0,
      "end_time": 917240.0,
      "text": "to build that trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 919120.0,
      "end_time": 920720.0,
      "text": "A lot of things have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 922440.0,
      "end_time": 925776.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to say what those six representatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 925800.0,
      "end_time": 927324.0,
      "text": "would have made of a smartphone."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 929000.0,
      "end_time": 930616.0,
      "text": "But in today&#39;s world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 930640.0,
      "end_time": 933256.0,
      "text": "as well as in their world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 933280.0,
      "end_time": 936400.0,
      "text": "competition makes the market work for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 938000.0,
      "end_time": 940256.0,
      "text": "And that is why I am convinced"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 940280.0,
      "end_time": 943456.0,
      "text": "that real and fair competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 943480.0,
      "end_time": 945536.0,
      "text": "has a vital role to play"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 945560.0,
      "end_time": 947736.0,
      "text": "in building the trust we need"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 947760.0,
      "end_time": 950880.0,
      "text": "to get the best of our societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 952000.0,
      "end_time": 956976.0,
      "text": "and that starts with enforcing our rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 957000.0,
      "end_time": 960816.0,
      "text": "actually just to make the market work for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 960840.0,
      "end_time": 962216.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 962240.0,
      "end_time": 965680.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 967760.0,
      "end_time": 969400.0,
      "text": "Bruno Giussani: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 971360.0,
      "end_time": 972616.0,
      "text": "Thank you, Commissioner."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 972640.0,
      "end_time": 974496.0,
      "text": "Margrethe Vestager: It was a pleasure."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 974520.0,
      "end_time": 976256.0,
      "text": "BG: I want to ask you two questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 976280.0,
      "end_time": 979160.0,
      "text": "The first one is about data, because I have the impression"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 979400.0,
      "end_time": 982456.0,
      "text": "that technology and data are changing the way competition takes place"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 982480.0,
      "end_time": 987136.0,
      "text": "and the way competition regulation is designed and enforced."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 987160.0,
      "end_time": 988815.0,
      "text": "Can you maybe comment on that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 988840.0,
      "end_time": 992176.0,
      "text": "MV: Well, yes, it is definitely challenging us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 992200.0,
      "end_time": 995416.0,
      "text": "because we both have to sharpen our tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 995440.0,
      "end_time": 997280.0,
      "text": "but also to develop new tools."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 998120.0,
      "end_time": 1000976.0,
      "text": "When we were going through the Google responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1001000.0,
      "end_time": 1003736.0,
      "text": "to our statement of objection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1003760.0,
      "end_time": 1007960.0,
      "text": "we were going through 5.2 terabytes of data."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1009800.0,
      "end_time": 1010600.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s quite a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1011320.0,
      "end_time": 1014616.0,
      "text": "So we had to set up new systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1014640.0,
      "end_time": 1017256.0,
      "text": "We had to figure out how to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1017280.0,
      "end_time": 1021376.0,
      "text": "because you cannot work the way you did just a few years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1021400.0,
      "end_time": 1025280.0,
      "text": "So we are definitely sharpening up our working methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1025880.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1028160.0000000001,
      "text": "The other thing is that we try to distinguish"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1028400.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1029735.0000000001,
      "text": "between different kinds of data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1029760.0,
      "end_time": 1032336.0,
      "text": "because some data is extremely valuable"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1032359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1035616.9999999999,
      "text": "and they will form, like, a barrier to entry in a market."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1035640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1039680.0000000001,
      "text": "Other things you can just -- it loses its value tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1040560.0,
      "end_time": 1042960.0,
      "text": "So we try to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1042119.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1045577.9999999999,
      "text": "that we never, ever underestimate the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1045599.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1049578.0,
      "text": "that data works as a currency in the market"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1049600.0,
      "end_time": 1054640.0,
      "text": "and as an asset that can be a real barrier for competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1055560.0,
      "end_time": 1060960.0,
      "text": "BG: Google. You fined them 2.8 billion euros a few months ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1060120.0,
      "end_time": 1062776.0,
      "text": "MV: No, that was dollars. It&#39;s not so strong these days."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1062800.0,
      "end_time": 1064296.0,
      "text": "BG: Ah, well, depends on the --"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1064320.0,
      "end_time": 1065336.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1065360.0,
      "end_time": 1067856.0,
      "text": "Google appealed the case. The case is going to court."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1067880.0,
      "end_time": 1069440.0,
      "text": "It will last a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1070240.0,
      "end_time": 1074976.0,
      "text": "Earlier, last year, you asked Apple to pay 13 billion in back taxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1075000.0,
      "end_time": 1078136.0,
      "text": "and you have also investigated other companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1078160.0,
      "end_time": 1080216.0,
      "text": "including European and Russian companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1080240.0,
      "end_time": 1082336.0,
      "text": "not only American companies, by far."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1082360.0,
      "end_time": 1086656.0,
      "text": "Yet the investigations against the American companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1086680.0,
      "end_time": 1089960.0,
      "text": "are the ones that have attracted the most attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1089120.0,
      "end_time": 1092136.0,
      "text": "and they have also attracted some accusations."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1092160.0,
      "end_time": 1095296.0,
      "text": "You have been accused, essentially, of protectionism, of jealousy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1095320.0,
      "end_time": 1098216.0,
      "text": "or using legislation to hit back at American companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1098240.0,
      "end_time": 1100536.0,
      "text": "that have conquered European markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1100560.0,
      "end_time": 1104150.0,
      "text": "\"The Economist\" just this week on the front page writes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1104400.0,
      "end_time": 1105936.0,
      "text": "\"Vestager Versus The Valley.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1105960.0,
      "end_time": 1107280.0,
      "text": "How do you react to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1108600.0,
      "end_time": 1111815.0,
      "text": "MV: Well, first of all, I take it very seriously,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1111840.0,
      "end_time": 1117159.0,
      "text": "because bias has no room in law enforcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1118160.0,
      "end_time": 1121336.0,
      "text": "We have to prove our cases with the evidence and the facts"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1121360.0,
      "end_time": 1123376.0,
      "text": "and the jurisprudence"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1123400.0,
      "end_time": 1125440.0,
      "text": "in order also to present it to the courts."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1126760.0,
      "end_time": 1130696.0,
      "text": "The second thing is that Europe is open for business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1130720.0,
      "end_time": 1132456.0,
      "text": "but not for tax evasion."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1132480.0,
      "end_time": 1136160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1138800.0,
      "end_time": 1142536.0,
      "text": "The thing is that we are changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1142560.0,
      "end_time": 1144775.0,
      "text": "and for instance, when I ask my daughters --"
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1144800.0,
      "end_time": 1146336.0,
      "text": "they use Google as well --"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1146360.0,
      "end_time": 1147856.0,
      "text": "\"Why do you do that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1147880.0,
      "end_time": 1150856.0,
      "text": "They say, \"Well, because it works. It&#39;s a very good product.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1150880.0,
      "end_time": 1153336.0,
      "text": "They would never, ever, come up with the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1153360.0,
      "end_time": 1155800.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s because it&#39;s a US product.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1155960.0,
      "end_time": 1157816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just because it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1157840.0,
      "end_time": 1159896.0,
      "text": "And that is of course how it should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1159920.0,
      "end_time": 1163336.0,
      "text": "But just the same, it is important that someone is looking after to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1163360.0,
      "end_time": 1165696.0,
      "text": "\"Well, we congratulate you"
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1165720.0,
      "end_time": 1168256.0,
      "text": "while you grow and grow and grow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1168280.0,
      "end_time": 1170160.0,
      "text": "but congratulation stops"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1170400.0,
      "end_time": 1172320.0,
      "text": "if we find that you&#39;re misusing your position"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 1174000.0,
      "end_time": 1178216.0,
      "text": "to harm competitors so that they cannot serve consumers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 1178240.0,
      "end_time": 1180336.0,
      "text": "BG: It will be a fascinating case to follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 1180360.0,
      "end_time": 1181735.0,
      "text": "Thank you for coming to TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 1181760.0,
      "end_time": 1183496.0,
      "text": "MV: It was a pleasure. Thanks a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 1183520.0,
      "end_time": 1187280.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}